import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='lat', kde=True, color='blue', label='lat')
    plt.axvline(data['lat'].median(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"Median: {data['lat'].median():.2f}")
    plt.title("What is the distribution of lat?", wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
